# Test Admin API - Kiểm tra API hoạt động

### 1. Login để lấy token mới
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123"
}

### 2. Kiểm tra user hiện tại (sau khi login)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Lấy danh sách users (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Lấy stats (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
